{
  "stem": "11998.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, Jacobi wants you to volunteer to go on this work trip.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And 400 men went with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they went to a camp in Germany, which is in Silesia, and they were treated very well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was an open camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They worked during the day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And at night, they could go into town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would barter with the farmers in the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they would actually send packages through the farmers to Sosnoweic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you know, they were paid money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so actually, our economic situation for the three or four months that he was away improved.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after the three months were up, they came back and they said, you know, that they're going to-- he must have been home maybe a week or two-- and then there was another decree from the Judenrat that said that they need 2,000 men.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well my father and all those 400 men were the first ones to volunteer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had an over-subscription, and they had people that they had to refuse because everybody wanted to go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The stories that they were bringing back with fantastic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And so they went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But this time already they, instead of being an open camp and being able to go to the city, there already were barbed wire and the SS-- or it was SR-- was in charge of their camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they were mistreated if they didn't work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were hit, and they were beaten if they were not producing for working fast enough.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Anyway, my father declared himself that he is ill.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they brought him back to Sosnoweic to examine him by the doctors.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
